<item>
            <title>[LU-8655] customize run_mdtest()</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-8655</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;sometimes it is required to run mdtest with parameters missing in run_mdtest()&lt;br/&gt;
Example: To reproduce some issue reported by our customers we needed to run:&lt;br/&gt;
mpirun -np 1 mdtest -n 100000 -i 1 -p 5 -u -v -F -d mdtest.out&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Proposed patch adds mdtest_custom_params, which allows to set mdtest_custom_params=&quot;-p 5 -F -v&quot; to run mdtest with required parameters,&lt;/p&gt;

</description>
